# 可数/不可数

好数/不好数(是否能够量化)

water(水)
money(钱)
fish(鱼)
fish(鱼肉)
coffee(变得可数了，默认为 cup)

# 介词 On

电器开关

(off 脱离)
(on  接触，进入某种状态 on line, on sale)

She turned me on at the first sight (一顾倾心)
on time (准时，on 0距离)
in time (期限內任一时刻)
call on

call at

Mongou on the North of Chian()
He stand on the head(倒立)

She turned me off (一顾作呕)
knock off (收工)
He has tried so hard to get a perfect kickoff. (开球)
offspring (弹出来，后代，血口喷人)

in the morning
on a rainy morning(更接近精准的时点)

about 转圈
On the theory of relativity (较聚焦)
About the theory of relativity (较浅)

# 考研英语语法核心考点(英语需要表句来表达感情)

三大从句: 
  名从
      主从
      表从
      同位语从句(对名词进行解释说明)
  定从
  状从
      when, as, since, until,
      before, after,
      where, because, since,
      thought, although, so that,
三种非谓语:
  动名词: V-ing
      做主语、宾语、表语
  不定式: to do
      除了不做(谓语&&同位语)
  分词  : V-ing; v-ed; 现在分词(主动)过去分词(被动)

四种特殊结构:
  比较结构看肯否
  倒装结构需还原
  分割结构找搭配
  省略结构省相同

# 主从 + 表从

What makes this slump different from the last is that there are still buyers in the market.

# 同位语从句

I, the most considerate girl in the world, love U.

A century ago, Freud formulated his revolutionary theory that dreams were the disguised shadows of our unconscious desires and fears.

# 定从

I love the boy who is handsome and generous.


# 三种特例(每一个引导词后都有一个从句)

定语从句引导词的省略(先行词在从句中作宾语):
This is the book I bought last week.

宾语从句引导词的省略(宾语从句的引导词为that):
I believe we will succeed.

And连接两个谓语动词:
She waved goodbye and walked ayaw in a hurry.

# 四种特殊结构

## 比较结构看肯否(not表部分否定，no表全部否定)

与其说...不如说...

A as ... as B:            She is as beautiful as her sister.
A more ... than B:        She is more beautiful than her sister.
                          与其说她的姐姐漂亮，不如说她漂亮。
A not more ... than B:    She is not more beautiful than her sister.
                          与其说她漂亮，不如说她的姐姐漂亮。
A no more ... than B:     She is no more beautiful than her sister.
                          她也不比她姐姐漂亮到哪里去
A not any more... than B: = no 

1. 划出比较连接词，确定肯否关系
2. 找出as或than之后的B，再确定与之结构相同的A
3. 按照肯否关系翻译，并调整语序(`肯定的放后面`)

But 
his primary task 
is `not` to think about 
the moral code 
    which governs his activity, 
`any more than`
a businessman 
is expected to dedicate 
his energies to an exploration of rules of conduct in business.

`any more than`的前后是对称的两个句子，都翻译成否定。
他的首要任务不是去思考道德准则，
就如同我们不能期待一个商人将其精力致力于商业运行规则的探索。

He is         more than a teacher.  他不仅仅是一个老师。
He is nothing more than a teacher.  他只不过是一个老师。
He is nothing less than a teacher.  他不仅仅是一个老师。

## 倒装结构需还原

Only in this way can we solve this problem. 找主语+找谓语+还原

Never will I marry you.                     全世界的男人都死光了，我也不嫁给你。

Were I a little bird, I would fly up high.  If I were a little bird, I would fly up high.


Only gradually 
was 
the by-product of the institution 
noted 
and 
only more gradually 
was 
this effect 
considered as a directive factor in the conduct of the institution.


## 分割结构找搭配

动宾分割: 及物动词 +...+ 名词

I 
shall define 
him as 
an individual 
    who
    has elected 
    as his primary duty and pleasure 
    in life 
    the activity of thinking in Socratic way about moral problems.

(他选择了)以苏格拉底方式思考道德问题的(活动)，作为其生活中的主要职责和乐趣。

## 省略结构省相同
